narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Greater understanding of the processes controlling high-latitude climate.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course was shaped by the interests of the participants and instructors, which was both a strength and a weakness. For example, I personally would have spent less time on sea ice and more time on other aspects of polar climates, but I understand that other students enjoyed the weeks of sea ice quite a bit.
